{name}:               first word of User.name
{test_url}:           url redirecting to tests for a given user and campaign
{cv_url}:             url redirecting to add cv for a given user
{sender_name}:        eg Santiago
{sender_position}:    eg CTO
{peaku_address}:      eg Calle blah
{campaign}:           Campaign.name
{video_url}:          url redirecting to add the video of the interview
{campaign_url}:       the url of a campaign.
{complete_name}:      The complete name ie: user.name
